P1para.Text:
In section 253(1)(b) of TCGA 1992 (which provides that a loan qualifies for relief only if the borrower is UK resident), at the beginning insert “
                if the loan is made before 24 January 2019,
              ”.

P3para.Text:
in the formula, after  “NBPLR +” insert “
                        NBTILR +
                      ”;

